cardchain.installBin:
cd $HOME
wget https://github.com/DecentralCardGame/Cardchain/releases/download/v0.10.0/Cardchaind
chmod 775 Cardchaind
sudo mv Cardchaind /usr/local/bin
cardchain.newInstallBin:
sudo systemctl stop Cardchaind
echo "export CARDCHAIN_CHAIN_ID="cardtestnet-5"" >> $HOME/.bash_profile
source $HOME/.bash_profile
wget -O $HOME/.Cardchain/config/genesis.json http://45.136.28.158:3000/genesis.json
Cardchaind tendermint unsafe-reset-all --home $HOME/.Cardchain
SEEDS=""
PEERS="109adfd1645cc1289bd2753277d6c5c2a9112b76@45.136.28.158:26656, 447a7af037dc85213d98ef3f4dc07d05191f52e7@202.61.225.157:26656"
sed -i -e "s/^seeds *=.*/seeds = \"$SEEDS\"/; s/^persistent_peers *=.*/persistent_peers = \"$PEERS\"/" $HOME/.Cardchain/config/config.toml
#config and start 
Cardchaind config chain-id cardtestnet-5
cd $HOME
wget https://github.com/DecentralCardGame/Cardchain/releases/download/v0.10.0/Cardchaind
chmod 775 Cardchaind
sudo mv Cardchaind /usr/local/bin
cardchain.desc: On Crowd Control you can create and design your own trading cards. Your Cards become a part of the game for everyone.

cascadia.installBin:
cd $HOME
rm -rf cascadia
git clone https://github.com/cascadiafoundation/cascadia
cd cascadia
git checkout v0.1.9
make install
cascadia.newInit:
cascadiad init $MONIKER --chain-id $CASCADIA_CHAIN_ID
# Config consensus parameters
sed -i -e "s/^timeout_propose *=.*/timeout_propose = \"3s\"/" $HOME/.cascadiad/config/config.toml
sed -i -e "s/^timeout_propose_delta *=.*/timeout_propose_delta = \"500ms\"/" $HOME/.cascadiad/config/config.toml
sed -i -e "s/^timeout_prevote *=.*/timeout_prevote = \"1s\"/" $HOME/.cascadiad/config/config.toml
sed -i -e "s/^timeout_prevote_delta *=.*/timeout_prevote_delta = \"500ms\"/" $HOME/.cascadiad/config/config.toml
sed -i -e "s/^timeout_precommit *=.*/timeout_precommit = \"1s\"/" $HOME/.cascadiad/config/config.toml
sed -i -e "s/^timeout_precommit_delta *=.*/timeout_precommit_delta = \"500ms\"/" $HOME/.cascadiad/config/config.toml
sed -i -e "s/^timeout_commit *=.*/timeout_commit = \"3s\"/" $HOME/.cascadiad/config/config.toml

celestia.installBin:
cd $HOME 
rm -rf celestia-app 
git clone https://github.com/celestiaorg/celestia-app.git 
cd celestia-app/ 
APP_VERSION=v1.3.0
git checkout tags/$APP_VERSION -b $APP_VERSION 
make install
cd $HOME
rm -rf networks
git clone https://github.com/celestiaorg/networks.git
celestia-appd init "test" --chain-id $CELESTIA_CHAIN_ID
cp $HOME/networks/mocha-4/genesis.json $HOME/.celestia-app/config
sed -i -e "s|^target_height_duration *=.*|timeout_commit = \"11s\"|" $HOME/.celestia-app/config/config.toml
celestia.newInstallBin:
cd $HOME 
rm -rf celestia-app 
git clone https://github.com/celestiaorg/celestia-app.git 
cd celestia-app/ 
APP_VERSION=v1.3.0
git checkout tags/$APP_VERSION -b $APP_VERSION 
make install
celestia.desc: Celestia is the first modular blockchain network. It is a modular consensus and data network, built to enable anyone to easily deploy their own blockchain with minimal overhead.
